headline.main: Glenn Ready for Orbit Wednesday; GLENN ORBIT SET FOR WEDNESDAY Technical Difficulties Soviet Flight Longer Last-Minute Decision

results.snippet: WASHINGTON, Jan. 20-- The United States hopes in the coming week to make its long-delayed attempt to send its first astronaut into orbit around the earth.

byline.original: By JOHN W. FINNEY Special to The New York Times

results.lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON, Jan. 20-- The United States hopes in the coming week to make its long-delayed attempt to send its first astronaut into orbit around the earth.
